---
---

<section class="cta-banner" data-reveal>
  <div class="cta-banner-inner">
    <div class="cta-banner-content">
      <h2>Got a conference, podcast or event? <span class="highlight">Let's talk.</span></h2>
      <p>I speak about AI in production, MLOps under real constraints, and building engineering teams that ship.</p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/speaking/">invite me to speak <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-banner {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 3rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 6rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .cta-banner-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-banner-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-banner-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 550px;
  }

  .cta-banner .btn {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-banner-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
